Class InventoryRestController

java.lang.Object
org.nejjari.hanae.gameup.web.SuperRestController<InventoryDto,InventoryService>
org.nejjari.hanae.gameup.web.rest.InventoryRestController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/inventory") public class InventoryRestController extends SuperRestController<InventoryDto,InventoryService>
REST controller for managing Inventory entities.

This controller provides endpoints for CRUD operations on Inventory resources. It extends the generic SuperRestController to inherit standard RESTful behavior.
